<lb n="0903c12"/><head type="no">No. 1381</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0903c13"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0903002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】麗本</note>佛說大吉祥陀羅尼經</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0903c14"/>
<lb n="0903c15"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0903003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（宋）＋西【明】</note><app n="0903003"><lem>西</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">宋西</rdg></app>天<note n="0903004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔譯經〕－【明】</note><app n="0903004"><lem>譯經</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>三藏朝散大夫試光祿卿
<lb n="0903c16"/>明教大師<note n="0903005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔臣〕－【明】</note><app n="0903005"><lem>臣</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>法賢奉　詔譯</byline>
<lb n="0903c17"/><p>如是我聞。一時佛在蘇珂&CB00085;帝佛剎。與諸大
<lb n="0903c18"/>菩薩并部多眾俱。爾時觀自在菩薩摩訶薩。
<lb n="0903c19"/>來詣佛所到已頭面禮足於一面坐。復有菩
<lb n="0903c20"/>薩摩訶薩名大吉祥。亦詣佛所到已繞佛三
<lb n="0903c21"/>匝。頭面禮足&CB00230;坐一面</p>
<lb n="0903c22"/><p>爾時世尊見大吉祥菩薩已。告觀自在菩薩
<lb n="0903c23"/>言。此大吉祥菩薩有陀羅尼。若閻浮提濁惡
<lb n="0903c24"/>世中。有比丘比丘尼優婆塞優婆夷等。見聞
<lb n="0903c25"/>隨喜讀誦受持。信解此法思惟記念。是貧苦
<lb n="0903c26"/>者獲大富貴。乃至部多普令愛敬。如是功德
<lb n="0903c27"/>不可具說。時觀自在菩薩聞佛<note n="0903006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">語＝說【明】</note><app n="0903006"><lem>語</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">說</rdg></app>已。歡喜踊
<lb n="0903c28"/>躍即從座起。合掌白佛言。世尊我今樂聞。唯
<lb n="0903c29"/>願世尊為我宣說</p>
<pb ed="T" id="T21.1381.0904a" n="0904a"/>
<lb n="0904a01"/><p>爾時世尊即說大吉祥陀羅尼曰</p>
<lb n="0904a02"/><p type="dharani">怛&CB00853;<note place="inline">切身下同</note>他<note place="inline">引一</note>洛叱彌<note place="inline">二合二</note>室哩<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00425;捺彌
<lb n="0904a03"/><note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00085;呬抳<note place="inline">引三</note>馱曩<note place="inline">引</note>提&CB00425;底<note place="inline">引四</note>藕哩<note place="inline">引五</note>摩
<lb n="0904a04"/>賀<note place="inline">引</note>野舍<note place="inline">引六</note>&CB00425;捺摩<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00135;怛哩<note place="inline">二合七</note>摩賀<note place="inline">引</note>
<lb n="0904a05"/>&CB00135;喻<note place="inline">二合</note>底<note place="inline">八</note>案曩那<note place="inline">引</note>曳<note place="inline">九</note>囉怛曩<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00425;囉
<lb n="0904a06"/><note place="inline">二合</note>婆摩賀<note place="inline">引</note>室哩<note place="inline">二合十</note>婆野替<note place="inline">引</note>那<note place="inline">十一</note>屹哩
<lb n="0904a07"/><note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00135;屹哩<note place="inline">二合</note>&CB00135;<note place="inline">十二</note>薩哩&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>遏迦哩也
<lb n="0904a08"/><note place="inline">二合</note>爍彌<note place="inline">引十三</note>提&CB00135;提&CB00135;<note place="inline">十四</note>悉悉悉悉<note place="inline">十五</note>&CB00135;
<lb n="0904a09"/>底&CB00135;底<note place="inline">十六</note>呬&CB00135;呬&CB00135;<note place="inline">十七</note>阿洛叉彌<note place="inline">二合十八</note>彌曩
<lb n="0904a10"/>舍野<note place="inline">十九</note>薩&CB00085;洛叉彌<note place="inline">二合</note>彌娑&CB00833;<note place="inline">切身引</note>那野莎
<lb n="0904a11"/><note place="inline">引</note>賀<note place="inline">二十</note>曩莫薩哩&CB00085;<note place="inline">二合</note>沒馱<note place="inline">二十一</note>冒提薩怛
<lb n="0904a12"/>吠<note place="inline">二合引</note>毘野<note place="inline">二合</note>莎<note place="inline">引</note>賀<note place="inline">引二十二</note></p>
<lb n="0904a13"/><p>爾時世尊說是經已。觀自在菩薩大吉祥菩
<lb n="0904a14"/>薩。并諸菩薩及部多眾。聞佛所說皆大歡喜
<lb n="0904a15"/>信受奉行</p>
<lb n="0904a16"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead>佛說大吉祥陀羅尼經</jhead></juan></div1>
